channel.title: Rebel Scape[release]
channel.description:
[center]Hello, i have been working on this source and im ready to release it. This is the first source release so please give some nice feedback on my work. I will release more work for the future. Please leave feedback.
[b]Home[/b] [URL=http://i675.photobucket.com/albums/vv118/ownerebel/rebelscapehome.jpg] Here [/URL]
[b]Train[/b] [URL=http://i675.photobucket.com/albums/vv118/ownerebel/rebelscapetrain.jpg] Here [/URL]
[b]Pkbox[/b] [URL=http://i675.photobucket.com/albums/vv118/ownerebel/rebelscapepkbox.jpg] Here [/URL]
[b]Vengance works[/b]
[b]Skill[/b] [URL=http://i675.photobucket.com/albums/vv118/ownerebel/rebelscapeskillz.jpg] Here [/URL]
[b]Guilds[/b] [URL=http://i675.photobucket.com/albums/vv118/ownerebel/rebelscapeguilds.jpg] Here [/URL]
[b]Shops[/b] [URL=http://i675.photobucket.com/albums/vv118/ownerebel/rebelscapeshop.jpg] Here [/URL]
[b]Barrows[/b] [URL=http://i675.photobucket.com/albums/vv118/ownerebel/rebelscapebarrows.jpg] Here [/URL]
Some sources that iv used in the past didnt have working crackers so i fixed them for everyone
http://i675.photobucket.com/albums/vv118/ownerebel/rebelscapecracker.jpg
http://i675.photobucket.com/albums/vv118/ownerebel/rebelscapefunpk.jpg
This is a pk based source with skills you can make the economy higher and kq drops rares :)
Download Link http://www.mediafire.com/?o3yznmgzjmu
This download comes with the client so its not going to be a 1 second download :D[/center] [center][b]Thank you zane02 for organizing this post.[/b]
[size=8][b] keep topic active by posting[/size]
[center][b]thank you to these 3 people for encouraging me to do a v2 [center]Jamie1200 [center]Jerome123183 [center]krackkid [center][size=2][b]No thanks to....[/size] [center]cows1471 [center]hpisavage
[center] Updates to come
[center]1.new home [center]2.new pk rewards example when 400 pk points reached you get automaticly bandos or a rare. that will probably be at 1000 pk points [center]3.new pk places [center]4.Adding all pvp armour and d claws [center]all the others will be posted on v3 [center][size=3][b]pm me suggestions
